query:
UPDATE AirQualityMetrics
SET
  node_id = $2,
  time = $3,
  pm10standard = $4,
  pm25standard = $5,
  pm100standard = $6,
  pm10environmental = $7,
  pm25environmental = $8,
  pm100environmental = $9,
  particles03um = $10,
  particles05um = $11,
  particles10um = $12,
  particles25um = $13,
  particles50um = $14,
  particles100um = $15,
  co2 = $16,
  sensor_type = $17
WHERE
  msg_id = $1
